{"tid":1405294,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"你地俾幾多錢家用","createTime":"2019-08-04T08:51:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T12:51:33.000Z","uid":12555,"like":41,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"c341bb69669e00fdefb4040bdb4691adee248d37","tid":1405294,"uid":12555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:51:42.000Z","msg":"最近轉咗工，家母又想向我索取家用，<br />\n<br />\n本身都俾開4k佢，屋企唔算拮据，<br />\n<br />\n阿哥老竇個啲都俾得多佢（大家夾埋20k)<br />\n<br />\n但佢就唔知成日就話生活費好貴，<br />\n<br />\n成9日講錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔知講開啲咩話題又會講咗家用好少嘅問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一講錢我又會同佢嘈，<br />\n<br />\n一唔夠人講就發爛渣講啲咩「養到你咁大」乜乜77，<br />\n<br />\n好似真係欠咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n成日口口聲聲話唔體諒佢，<br />\n<br />\n但你有無尊重過人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講嘢又難聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你地俾幾多家用？<br />\n有無巴絲老竇老母都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ead596118011976eac20b2b5a2f0c11d38685f2e","tid":1405294,"uid":92552,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:16:25.000Z","msg":"出黎做野差不多一年 暫時比5k<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"052e60a0d7fda557835b5b50203c5b77b700653b","tid":1405294,"uid":51827,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:23:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e00dfa00d32d157625e1456e8a3cd886b1156e85","tid":1405294,"uid":113085,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T11:25:22.000Z","msg":"0<br />\n應該屌番佢，人地老豆老母比首期，你有冇呀?"},{"pid":"b1616484ebe68ee36893b38be2232b530481c7b2","tid":1405294,"uid":12555,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"052e60a0d7fda557835b5b50203c5b77b700653b","tid":14